聆听披头士乐队的“最后”歌曲“Now And Then” https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-the-beatles-final-song-now-and-then-3529039?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=listen-to-the-beatles-final-歌曲现在和那时Liberty DunworthThu, 02 Nov 2023 14:00:27 +0000 Music NewsNewsPopRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3529039 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/The-Beatles@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="披头士乐队参加在经理布莱恩·爱泼斯坦 (Brian Epstein) 家中举行的新闻发布会，支持释放中士。佩珀的孤独之心俱乐部乐队，1967 年 5 月 19 日" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/The-Beatles@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/The-Beatles@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/The-Beatles@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/The-Beatles@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/The-Beatles@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/The-Beatles@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这首歌是最后一首以披头士四人组所有原始成员为特色的歌曲</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-the-beatles-final-song-now-and-then-3529039">聆听披头士乐队的“最后”歌曲《Now And Then》一文</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/The-Beatles@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="披头士乐队参加在经理布莱恩·爱泼斯坦 (Brian Epstein) 家中举行的新闻发布会，支持释放中士。佩珀的孤独之心俱乐部乐队，1967 年 5 月 19 日" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/The-Beatles@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/The-Beatles@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/The-Beatles@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/The-Beatles@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/The-Beatles@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/The-Beatles@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>经过几个月的等待，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paul-mccartney">保罗·麦卡特尼</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ringo-starr">林戈·斯塔尔</a>分享了《Now And Then》，这是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-beatles">披头士乐队</a>所有四位原始成员的最后一首歌曲。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-beatles-every-song-ranked-3121214">披头士乐队：每首歌按伟大程度排列</a></strong></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paul-mccartney-says-artificial-intelligence-has-enabled-a-final-beatles-song-3455297">早在六月份，麦卡特尼就首次透露了</a>这个备受期待的项目，当时他确认自己正在与鼓手合作创作一首新曲目，这将成为乐队唱片中的“最后”歌曲。</p><p>这张专辑名为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-beatles-final-ai-song-now-and-then-blue-red-album-reissues-trailer-documentary-3522051">《Now And Then》</a> ，源自已故乐队成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/john-lennon">约翰·列侬 (John Lennon)</a>录制的演示磁带，并在人工智能的帮助下完成，人工智能将歌曲作者的声音从最初的录音中剔除出来，并允许幸存的成员与他们一起工作。</p><p>自从第一次分享这首歌的细节以来，麦卡特尼和斯塔尔<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ringo-starr-says-final-beatles-track-assisted-by-ai-should-have-been-out-already-3508409">几个月来一直在不断地调侃即将到来的项目</a>。其中包括后者透露他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ringo-starr-last-beatles-song-created-with-ai-beautiful-track-3469906">认为这个项目“很漂亮”</a> ，后来又承认制作单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ringo-starr-says-making-final-beatles-song-was-like-having-john-lennon-back-3526791">“就像约翰·列侬回来了一样”</a> 。</p><p>他们还暗示，该项目将于上周即将到来，当时他们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/are-the-beatles-teasing-the-release-of-their-final-song-3521300">在社交媒体和互联网上发布了盒式磁带的图像</a>，以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-beatles-continue-to-tease-final-song-with-projections-across-liverpool-3521832">四巨头家乡利物浦的投影</a>。</p><p>昨晚（11 月 1 日）， <em>The One Show</em>和乐队的 YouTube 频道播放了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-the-beatles-short-film-now-and-then-the-last-beatles-song-3528193">一部短片</a>，记录了这首歌背后的历史以及它是如何组合在一起的。</p><p>看看下面的歌曲。 </p><p><iframe title="Spotify 嵌入：现在和那时" style="border-radius: 12px" width="100%" height="152" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" loading="lazy" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/track/4vziJcnB2Qyi9o4nIRUeN7?si=7211776ca7024527&#038;utm_source=oembed"></iframe></p><p>您可以在此处观看上述令人心酸的 12 分钟影片，该影片也<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-bbc-to-celebrate-the-beatles-following-announcement-of-now-and-then-3522728">作为 BBC 庆祝披头士乐队遗产的系列节目的一部分</a>播出。</p><p>在视频中，麦卡特尼回忆了 70 年代末列侬如何在纽约的家中首次创作并录制了《Now And Then》的小样，其中只有他的钢琴和歌声。在他去世后，他的妻子<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yoko-ono">小野洋子 (Yoko Ono)</a>于 1994 年将这张唱片以及《Free As A Bird》和《Real Love》的小样交给了麦卡特尼、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/george-harrison">乔治·哈里森</a>和斯塔尔。</p><p>后两首歌曲均在 90 年代中期作为披头士乐队“选集”项目的一部分作为“新”披头士曲目发行。</p><p>幸存的成员与制作人杰夫·林恩 (Jeff Lynne) 一起录制了新的部分，并完成了《Now And Then》的粗略混音，但该项目最终被搁置，因为“技术限制”意味着列侬的歌声和钢琴无法分开以获得足够清晰的混合。 </p><figure id="attachment_3529042" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3529042" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3529042" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/the-beatles-bw@2000x1270.jpg" alt="1966 年 6 月 17 日，英国流行乐队披头士乐队世界巡演开始前在伦敦 BBC 电视演播室拍摄的肖像。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/the-beatles-bw@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/the-beatles-bw@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/the-beatles-bw@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/the-beatles-bw@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/the-beatles-bw@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/the-beatles-bw@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3529042" class="wp-caption-text"> 1966 年 6 月 17 日，英国流行乐队披头士乐队在伦敦 BBC 电视演播室开始世界巡演前的肖像。图片来源：Central Press/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>麦卡特尼在视频中表示：“我们花了近四分之一个世纪的时间才等到合适的时机再次处理‘现在和那时’。”他解释说，与彼得·杰克逊在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/tv-reviews/the-beatles-get-back-review-3103706">2021 年的<em>《归来》</em>纪录片系列</a>中的合作让他想要重新访问曲目并重试。</p><p>该曲目现已与他们 1962 年的首张英国单曲“Love Me Do”一起作为双 A 面进行销售，该单曲将他们的第一首单曲与最后一首单曲结合在一起。</p><p>一段音乐视频——这将是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/peter-jackson-to-direct-music-video-for-final-beatles-song-using-newly-unearthed-footage-3526878">彼得·杰克逊执导的第一部音乐视频</a>——也将于明天（11 月 3 日）发布。据这位著名电影制作人称，视觉伴奏将包括麦卡特尼和斯塔尔的新镜头，以及最近出土的所有四位成员的镜头。</p><p>此外，下周（11 月 10 日）披头士乐队将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-beatles-final-ai-song-now-and-then-blue-red-album-reissues-trailer-documentary-3522051">发行“1962-1966（红色专辑）”和“1967-1970（蓝色专辑）”的新扩展版本</a>，以立体声和杜比混合。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-the-beatles-final-song-now-and-then-3529039">聆听披头士乐队的“最后”歌曲《Now And Then》一文</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
詹姆斯·邦德游戏“007计划”被称为“终极间谍幻想” https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/james-bond-game-project-007-said-to-be-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy-3529009?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=james-邦德游戏项目 007 据说是终极间谍奇幻作品Imogen DonovanThu, 02 Nov 2023 13:49:31 +0000 Gaming NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3529009 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/project-007-is-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/project-007-is-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/project-007-is-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/project-007-is-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/project-007-is-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/project-007-is-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/project-007-is-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这更像是“丹尼尔·克雷格而不是罗杰·摩尔”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/james-bond-game-project-007-said-to-be-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy-3529009">被称为“终极间谍幻想”的后詹姆斯·邦德游戏“Project 007”</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/project-007-is-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/project-007-is-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/project-007-is-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/project-007-is-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/project-007-is-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/project-007-is-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/project-007-is-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/io-interactive">IO Interactive</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/james-bond"><em>詹姆斯·邦德</em></a>游戏<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/project-007"><em>《Project 007》</em></a>被称为“终极间谍幻想”，暗示了沉浸式模拟的元素。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/avatar-frontiers-of-pandora-preview-far-cry-james-cameron-3522152">《阿凡达：潘多拉边境》为詹姆斯·卡梅隆的史诗片增添了“孤岛惊魂”的元素</a></strong></li></ul><p><em>《杀手》</em>开发商<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/hitman-devs-are-working-on-a-james-bond-game-2820823">在 2020 年透露</a>，确认<em>《Project 007》</em>将讲述一个“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/io-interactives-project-007-will-feature-an-original-story-2914521">完全原创的故事</a>”，不会消除原著或电影的影响。</p><p> “我们能够创建数字债券非常重要。游戏行业的债券，”当时的首席执行官兼共同所有者哈坎·阿布兰 (Hakan Abran) 说道。 </p><figure id="attachment_3529052" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3529052" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3529052" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/project-007-is-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/project-007-is-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/project-007-is-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/project-007-is-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/project-007-is-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/project-007-is-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/project-007-is-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3529052" class="wp-caption-text"> 《杀手 3》来源：IO Interactive</figcaption></figure><p> “每一部邦德都定义了一代人，令人惊奇的是他们多年来不断重塑自己。”</p><p>从那时起，关于<em>007 计划的</em>细节一直没有公开，但最新一期<em>《Edge》</em>杂志对 Abran 的采访已经让粉丝们了解了一些期待。</p><p> “我们在办公室里能找到的少数其他线索表明，其语气更接近丹尼尔·克雷格而不是罗杰·摩尔，而且也许是比<em>《杀手</em>》的自由短途更加脚本化的体验，”该杂志解释道（来自<a href="https://www.gamesradar.com/upcoming-james-bond-game-project-007-is-being-described-as-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Games Radar</em></a> ）。</p><p> “它被定位为‘终极间谍幻想’，暗示着一些小玩意——也许距离《特工 47》的凶残目标只有一步之遥。” </p><figure id="attachment_3529054" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3529054" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3529054" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/project-007-is-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy-3.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/project-007-is-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy-3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/project-007-is-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy-3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/project-007-is-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy-3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/project-007-is-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy-3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/project-007-is-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy-3-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/project-007-is-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy-3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3529054" class="wp-caption-text"> 《杀手 3》来源：IO Interactive</figcaption></figure><p>因此，这似乎暗示了一种更现代的背景和基调，其灵感来自全球化世界的焦虑，技术触及公民和间谍周围。</p><p>此外，“终极间谍幻想”的措辞可能被解释为与对周围环境做出反应并操纵周围环境以完成任务有关。</p><p>沉浸式模拟，如<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/deus-ex">《杀出重围》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/dishonored">《耻辱》</a></em>和<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/system-shock">《网络奇兵》</a></em>系列，不会向玩家强调他们应该以特定方式实现目标。</p><p>如果<em>《007计划》</em>中的詹姆斯·邦德能够使用大量可以致命或非致命消灭敌人的装备（用“间谍技术”来暗示），那么听起来游戏体验可能会比《<em>杀手》</em>系列更加灵活。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/starfield-to-roll-out-a-much-anticipated-feature-in-steam-beta-next-week-3528930"><em>Starfield</em>将在未注明日期的更新中添加 Nvidia DLSS 支持</a>，并宣布 AMD FSR 3 也即将推出。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/james-bond-game-project-007-said-to-be-the-ultimate-spycraft-fantasy-3529009">被称为“终极间谍幻想”的后詹姆斯·邦德游戏“Project 007”</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
